        "start_offset": 95,
        "end_offset": 270,
        "start": 20.821,
        "end": 75.725
      },
      {
        "segment": "The activity of dreaming is an activity in which there is made a finely wrought and excellently fashioned bridge from conscious to unconscious.",
        "start_offset": 271,
        "end_offset": 414,
        "start": 79.466,
        "end": 117.888
      },
      {
        "segment": "In this state the various distortions which have occurred in the energy web of the body complex, due to the misprecision with which energy influxes have been received, are healed.",
