        "start_offset": 670,
        "end_offset": 762,
        "start": 192.533,
        "end": 220.595
      },
      {
        "segment": "The other function of the dreaming which is of aid is that type of dream which is visionary and which prophets and mystics have experienced from days of old.",
        "start_offset": 763,
        "end_offset": 920,
        "start": 226.296,
        "end": 267.399
      },
      {
        "segment": "Their visions come through the roots of mind and speak to a hungry world.",
        "start_offset": 921,
        "end_offset": 994,
        "start": 270.459,
        "end": 286.8
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus the dream is of service without being of a personally polarizing nature.",
        "start_offset": 995,
        "end_offset": 1072,
        "start": 288.94,
        "end": 309.002
      },
      {
